Class ExoticAnimal

java.lang.Object
petadoption.model.Pet
petadoption.model.ExoticAnimal
public class ExoticAnimal extends Pet
ExoticAnimal is a subclass of Pet that represents animals not typically categorized as standard pets. This class holds additional fields unique to exotic species.
